title.rendered: Wolfgang Grenke – Lurking in the Shadows

content.rendered: Wolfgang Grenke sends Viceroy read-reply email receipt, confirming he has not removed himself from the company, and CTP is inherently intertwined and controlled by Grenke AG group and its insiders.
